                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَأَوْجَسَ مِنْهُمْ﴾ أَحَسَّ فِي نَفْسِهِ مِنْهُمْ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بِغُلاَمٍ﴾ هُوَ: إِسْحَاقُ عليه السلام.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "51:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿امْرَأَتُهُ﴾ هِيَ: سَارَةُ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿صَرَّةٍ﴾ صَيْحَةٍ، وَضَجَّةٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَصَكَّتْ وَجْهَهَا﴾ لَطَمَتْهُ بِيَدِهَا تَعَجُّبًا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿عَقِيمٌ﴾ لاَ يُولَدُ لِي وَلَدٌ.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
